{"tid":1579294,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【哪有錢？】香港人究竟要儲幾多錢，先會覺得有足夠安全感？","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T16:25:21.000Z","uid":57424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8b915300a594eb70a8194847e0c67e234caf65fb","tid":1579294,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"香港存款保障委員會委託香港民意研究所，喺上個月以電話隨機訪問1000名18歲或以上香港市民，發現當中有65%市民有儲蓄習慣，而每人每月平均儲蓄金額比舊年微升7%，中位數係5000元。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦都發現，受訪者對目前擁有嘅儲蓄所帶嚟嘅安全感評分係56.1分，同舊年55.5分差唔多。其中18至29歲受訪者對儲蓄嘅評分最高，有57.9分，並且覺得有49萬元儲蓄就足夠；70歲或以上受訪者安全感最低，只有53.5分，而且認為儲到60萬元先安心。即將退休嘅50至65歲人士就認為，退休要有近524萬元儲蓄先會有足夠安全感。<br />\n<br />\n存保會主席許敬文就話，香港人儲蓄金額雖然上升咗，但整體有呢個習慣嘅市民比例就稍為下降，更多市民話無定到每年儲錢目標，反映港人對儲蓄未必有周詳計劃或具體行動。"},{"pid":"7721df91d0af7022b7ea5de98eb8fe8d0d03dc84","tid":1579294,"uid":185449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"拎住舊錢冇意思 <br />\n退休起碼要有一層自住樓+一層收租樓先叫入門級<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ff2af4830f330f6483ba505665723d78137b44","tid":1579294,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"60萬做到咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6255ba79edbb14d3df33753761a2d480df7db4","tid":1579294,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83624126aee46544be12fc0c3f156653ee4c689","tid":1579294,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"60萬有咩安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dec661004bb78176446e89956b25eb3292e162","tid":1579294,"uid":233929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"6000萬會安心少少"},{"pid":"b13f6493ab3762eb94461ffdda5382d4ebde72ca","tid":1579294,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"60萬隨時變廢紙嘅港幣 仲講咩安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccc883c3ac36da5bb23b54230d33b3b89531b84","tid":1579294,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"43bd6b50872c2e383dfbffa15627edc490234aaa","tid":1579294,"uid":270563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ac74dc29b619ef962c0b3aaced44a9424129466","tid":1579294,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">70歲或以上受訪者安全感最低，只有53.5分，而且認為儲到60萬元先安心。</span><br />\n每個月得幾千蚊咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc1fae8c1d75da67e8594920098ddbbe9af5969","tid":1579294,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"60萬講70以上姐<br />\n最壞情況都實有公屋住<br />\n同埋有病都唔醫啦<br />\n<br />\n其實夠既"},{"pid":"48757cdf18973ca6c903dcdf9c5e8a036a8f0e95","tid":1579294,"uid":49342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"反而一個月儲5000其實有乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}